---
import "../../styles.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About | Fiqry Firmansyah</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Outfit:wght@500;700;900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body data-home-only>
    <header class="site-header">
      <a class="brand" href="/">FIQRY FIRMANSYAH</a>
      <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Navigasi utama">
        <a href="/#home">Home</a>
        <a class="active" href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/#projects">Project</a>
        <a href="/#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="about-page about-complete-page">
      <a class="project-back-icon about-back-icon" href="/#about" aria-label="Kembali ke home about">
        <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </a>

      <section class="about-hero about-complete-hero">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">About Me</p>
        <h1>I design and build clean digital interfaces with responsive detail.</h1>
        <p>
          Saya fokus membuat website yang ringan, rapi, dan nyaman digunakan di berbagai ukuran
          layar. Saya suka menggabungkan struktur frontend yang jelas, visual yang modern, dan detail
          interaksi kecil agar halaman terasa hidup tanpa berlebihan.
        </p>
        <div class="about-hero-meta" aria-label="Profile summary">
          <span><strong>Frontend</strong> Main Focus</span>
          <span><strong>Responsive</strong> Layout Detail</span>
          <span><strong>Visual</strong> UI Polish</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-profile-grid">
        <article class="about-detail-card about-profile-card about-story-card">
          <p class="section-eyebrow">Profile</p>
          <h2>Tentang Saya</h2>
          <div class="about-story-body">
            <p>
              Saya tertarik pada frontend development karena menggabungkan logika, estetika, dan
              pengalaman pengguna. Dalam setiap project, saya berusaha membuat tampilan yang tidak
              hanya bagus dilihat, tetapi juga rapi secara struktur dan nyaman digunakan.
            </p>
            <p>
              Saat membuat halaman, saya memperhatikan hierarchy, spacing, warna, responsive behavior,
              dan konsistensi komponen. Tujuannya sederhana: pengguna bisa memahami isi halaman dengan
              cepat dan merasa nyaman saat menjelajahinya.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-story-stats" aria-label="About highlights">
            <span><strong>UI</strong> Clean interface</span>
            <span><strong>UX</strong> Easy to scan</span>
            <span><strong>Code</strong> Structured build</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="about-detail-card about-focus-card about-priority-card">
          <p class="section-eyebrow">What I Care About</p>
          <h2>Fokus Kerja</h2>
          <ol class="about-priority-list">
            <li>
              <span>01</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Clean layout structure</strong>
                <p>Susunan section jelas, spacing konsisten, dan informasi mudah discan.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span>02</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Responsive detail</strong>
                <p>Tampilan tetap proporsional dari mobile sampai layar desktop besar.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span>03</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Visual consistency</strong>
                <p>Warna, typography, card, dan state dibuat senada antar halaman.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section-block">
        <div class="about-section-heading">
          <p class="section-eyebrow">Skills</p>
          <h2>Skill dan tools yang saya gunakan.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="about-skill-grid about-modern-skill-grid">
          <article class="about-detail-card about-modern-skill-card">
            <span class="skill-index">01</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Frontend</h3>
              <p>Membangun halaman web dengan HTML semantik, CSS yang terstruktur, Astro, dan JavaScript seperlunya.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-cloud">
              <span>Astro</span>
              <span>HTML</span>
              <span>CSS</span>
              <span>JavaScript</span>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="about-detail-card about-modern-skill-card">
            <span class="skill-index">02</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Design Implementation</h3>
              <p>Menerjemahkan referensi desain menjadi tampilan web yang rapi, proporsional, dan konsisten.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-cloud">
              <span>Figma</span>
              <span>UI Layout</span>
              <span>Spacing</span>
              <span>Typography</span>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="about-detail-card about-modern-skill-card">
            <span class="skill-index">03</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Responsive Polish</h3>
              <p>Menyesuaikan tampilan untuk mobile, tablet, laptop, dan desktop besar tanpa membuat layout terasa aneh.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-cloud">
              <span>Mobile-first</span>
              <span>Grid</span>
              <span>Flexbox</span>
              <span>Testing</span>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section-block about-list-duo">
        <article class="about-detail-card about-list-card">
          <p class="section-eyebrow">Experience</p>
          <h2>Pengalaman</h2>
          <ul class="about-simple-list">
            <li>
              <span>01</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Portfolio & Landing Page</strong>
                <p>Membangun halaman personal branding, landing page, dan UI presentasi project.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span>02</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Responsive Interface</strong>
                <p>Menyesuaikan layout untuk desktop, tablet, dan mobile dengan detail spacing.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span>03</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Design Implementation</strong>
                <p>Menerjemahkan referensi visual/Figma menjadi halaman web yang hidup.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span>04</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Project Presentation</strong>
                <p>Mengemas karya web dan photography melalui card, gallery, dan halaman detail.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="about-detail-card about-list-card">
          <p class="section-eyebrow">Certification</p>
          <h2>Sertifikasi</h2>
          <ul class="about-simple-list">
            <li>
              <span>2026</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Frontend Development Fundamentals</strong>
                <p>Dasar HTML, CSS, JavaScript, responsive design, dan struktur halaman web.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span>2026</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Responsive Web Design</strong>
                <p>Prinsip layout adaptif, grid, breakpoint, typography, dan pengujian lintas device.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span>2026</span>
              <div>
                <strong>UI Design Practice</strong>
                <p>Penerapan hierarchy, spacing, warna, komposisi, dan detail visual interface.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="about-closing-card">
        <div>
          <p class="section-eyebrow">Current Direction</p>
          <h2>Terus berkembang di frontend dan visual presentation.</h2>
        </div>
        <a class="secondary-button" href="/#projects">Lihat Project</a>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer-simple">
      <a class="brand" href="/">FIQRY FIRMANSYAH</a>
      <p>Frontend developer and photography enthusiast.</p>
      <nav aria-label="Footer navigation">
        <a href="/#home">Home</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/#projects">Project</a>
        <a href="/#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </footer>

    <script is:inline>
      const root = document.documentElement;
      const themeToggle = document.querySelector("[data-theme-toggle]");
      const themeLabel = document.querySelector("[data-theme-label]");

      function setTheme(theme) {
        root.dataset.theme = theme;
        localStorage.setItem("theme", theme);
        if (themeLabel) themeLabel.textContent = theme === "night" ? "Night" : "Light";
      }

      setTheme(localStorage.getItem("theme") || "night");

      themeToggle?.addEventListener("click", () => {
        setTheme(root.dataset.theme === "night" ? "light" : "night");
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
